---
// src/pages/cheatsheets.astro
// Landingpage für Python Cheat Sheet Downloads
---

<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Python Cheat Sheets – Kostenloser Download | PhilsDevQuest</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Kostenlose Python Cheat Sheets zum Download – Anfänger und Fortgeschrittene. Alle wichtigen Konzepte auf einen Blick, im PhilsDevQuest Earthy Warm Design."
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@400;600;700&family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg-base: #12100e;
        --bg-elevated: #1c1916;
        --bg-overlay: #252018;
        --terracotta: #c1634f;
        --terracotta-l: #d4816b;
        --sand: #d4a96a;
        --cream: #e8c99a;
        --orange: #ff6b35;
        --text-primary: #e8e0d8;
        --text-sec: #b5a99a;
        --text-muted: #7a6e63;
        --border: rgba(232, 224, 216, 0.1);
      }

      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        background: var(--bg-base);
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* ── Hero ── */
      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 64px 24px 48px;
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: rgba(193, 99, 79, 0.15);
        color: var(--terracotta);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(193, 99, 79, 0.25);
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 54px);
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .hero h1 em {
        color: var(--terracotta);
        font-style: inherit;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-sec);
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 540px;
        margin: 0 auto 12px;
      }

      .hero-note {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .hero-note::before {
        content: "";
        display: inline-block;
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        background: #4caf50;
        border-radius: 50%;
      }

      /* ── Divider ── */
      .divider {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 48px;
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      /* ── Cards Container ── */
      .cards {
        max-width: 860px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px 80px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .cards {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      /* ── Download Card ── */
      .card {
        background: var(--bg-elevated);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition:
          border-color 0.2s,
          transform 0.2s;
      }

      .card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(193, 99, 79, 0.35);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .card-header {
        padding: 24px 24px 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .card-level {
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .card-level.beginner {
        color: var(--terracotta);
      }
      .card-level.advanced {
        color: var(--sand);
      }

      .card h2 {
        font-family: "Caveat", cursive;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .card p {
        font-size: 12.5px;
        color: var(--text-sec);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .card-body {
        padding: 20px 24px;
      }

      /* Topics list */
      .topics {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 7px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .topic {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 9px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-sec);
      }

      .topic-dot {
        width: 5px;
        height: 5px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .beginner-dot {
        background: var(--terracotta);
      }
      .advanced-dot {
        background: var(--sand);
      }

      /* Meta info */
      .card-meta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 18px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .meta-item {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2px;
      }

      .meta-label {
        font-size: 10px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      }

      .meta-value {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
      }

      /* Download button */
      .btn-download {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 10px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 13px 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
      }

      .btn-download:hover {
        opacity: 0.88;
      }

      .btn-beginner {
        background: var(--terracotta);
        color: #12100e;
      }

      .btn-advanced {
        background: var(--sand);
        color: #12100e;
      }

      .btn-icon {
        width: 16px;
        height: 16px;
        fill: currentColor;
      }

      /* ── Info Section ── */
      .info {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px 64px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .info h3 {
        font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 400;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .info p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .info code {
        background: rgba(232, 224, 216, 0.08);
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--cream);
      }

      /* ── Back link ── */
      .back {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 0 0 40px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .back:hover {
        color: var(--terracotta);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-badge">🎁 Kostenloser Download</div>
      <h1><em>Python Cheat Sheets</em><br />Alle Konzepte auf einen Blick</h1>
      <p>
        Kompakte Referenzkarten im PhilsDevQuest Design — von Variablen bis
        Context Manager. Einfach herunterladen, ausdrucken, und griffbereit
        haben.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-note">
        Kostenlos · Kein Account nötig · Teilen erwünscht
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="cards">
      <!-- Anfänger -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-level beginner">🐍 Anfänger</div>
          <h2>Python Grundlagen</h2>
          <p>
            Alles was du für den Einstieg brauchst — von Variablen bis Module.
            Perfekt zum Ausdrucken und neben den Monitor legen.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Seiten</span>
              <span class="meta-value">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Themen</span>
              <span class="meta-value">12</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Sprache</span>
              <span class="meta-value">Deutsch</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Variablen &amp;
              Datentypen
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Strings &amp; Listen
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Bedingungen &amp;
              Schleifen
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Funktionen &amp;
              Dictionaries
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Fehlerbehandlung &amp;
              Module
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot beginner-dot"></span>Operatoren &amp;
              Built-ins
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/downloads/python-cheatsheet-anfaenger.pdf"
            download
            class="btn-download btn-beginner"
          >
            <svg
              class="btn-icon"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path d="M12 16l-6-6h4V4h4v6h4l-6 6zm-8 2h16v2H4v-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            PDF herunterladen
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Fortgeschritten -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-level advanced">🚀 Fortgeschritten</div>
          <h2>Python Vertiefung</h2>
          <p>
            Für alle die über die Grundlagen hinausgehen wollen — von List
            Comprehensions bis Context Manager. Mit vollständigen
            Code-Beispielen.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-meta">
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Seiten</span>
              <span class="meta-value">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Themen</span>
              <span class="meta-value">12</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item">
              <span class="meta-label">Sprache</span>
              <span class="meta-value">Deutsch</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>List Comprehensions
              &amp; Lambda
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>*args, **kwargs &amp;
              Klassen
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>Vererbung &amp;
              Decorators
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>Generators &amp; File
              I/O
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>Dataclasses &amp; Dict
              Tricks
            </div>
            <div class="topic">
              <span class="topic-dot advanced-dot"></span>f-Strings &amp;
              Context Manager
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/downloads/python-cheatsheet-fortgeschritten.pdf"
            download
            class="btn-download btn-advanced"
          >
            <svg
              class="btn-icon"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path d="M12 16l-6-6h4V4h4v6h4l-6 6zm-8 2h16v2H4v-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            PDF herunterladen
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info -->
    <section class="info">
      <h3>Wie drucke ich das am besten?</h3>
      <p>
        PDF öffnen → Drucken → Papierformat <code>A4</code> → Ränder <code
          >Keine</code
        > → Hintergrundgrafiken <code>aktivieren</code>
      </p>
      <p>
        Für den Bildschirm: einfach die PDF-Datei speichern und in jedem
        PDF-Reader öffnen.
      </p>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="back">← Zurück zur Startseite</a>
  </body>
</html>
